snippet.textDisplay:
The Singer is representing *Punjabi* Muslims at centre stage singing in Punjabi language & trying to communicate other muslim cultures of subcountinent.

1)The Lady in Saree represent *Bengali* Muslim culture.
2)The Lady sitting near Flowers represent *Kashmiri* Muslim culture.
3)The Lady with 2 pony tails & the group of dancers represent *Sindhi* Muslim culture.
4)The Boy at the end dance represent the Leva dance of *Balochistan*
5)The Boy sitting & playing Rabab represents *Pashtun* culture.
